!! Final Notes

This test tiddler covers:

* All heading levels
* All text formatting (bold, italic, underline, strikethrough, superscript, subscript)
* All list types (bullet, numbered, definition, mixed, quoted)
* All link types (wiki, external, image, CamelCase, system, auto-URL)
* Transclusions (simple, field, index, filtered)
* Macros (simple, parameterized, nested)
* Widgets (comprehensive coverage of common widgets)
* HTML elements (basic, with attributes, nested, self-closing)
* Tables (simple, headers, footers, captions, classes, merged cells)
* Code blocks (plain, with language, inline)
* Typed blocks
* Block quotes (simple, with class, with citation)
* Horizontal rules
* Dashes (en-dash, em-dash)
* HTML entities
* Escape sequences
* Comments
* Pragmas (define, procedure, function, widget, whitespace, rules, import)
* Conditional syntax (if, else, elseif, nested)
* Highlighting/styled text
* Filter expressions (all operators and run prefixes)
* All attribute types (string, indirect, macro, filter, substituted, boolean)
* Variable substitution
* Placeholder parameters
* Edge cases and special situations
* Unicode support
* Complex nested examples

